{"tid":2375136,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"三十秒科學–貓草","createTime":"2021-01-21T20:31:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-23T15:40:10.000Z","uid":38861,"like":118,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"d2c3f3a70de121d5cab86b268e8016ffe76c974c","tid":2375136,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T20:31:41.000Z","msg":"貓隻遇到貓草後，不但會舔草，亦會用頭及臉與草磨擦，甚至會以全身的方式在草上滾動。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k4Q1JL5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk4Q1JL5.jpg&h=63b23f79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n過程通常歷時5-15分鐘，然後就會有以小時計的冷靜期。<br />\n<br />\n究竟，貓草的吸引力在於哪裡呢?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖2）有日本科學家從貓草中提煉出一種科學物質Nepetalactol。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a8M8oMa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa8M8oMa.jpg&h=3603e30a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在18隻本身對貓草有正面反應的貓隻中，有15隻主動走向含Nepetalactol的紙張上，利用身體跟其磨擦，歷時接近10分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）有圖有真相，實驗室的貓，流浪貓，就連豹及美洲獅都屈服在貓草的Nepetalactol化學物質上。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s9KRmx4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs9KRmx4.png&h=3107090e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然而，狗隻及老鼠則對這化學質並無興趣。<br />\n<br />\n（圖4）經過一系列的實驗後，證實貓隻吸入貓草的Nepetalactol化學物質後，血液的&beta;-endorphin份量會隨之上升，導致愉悅感增加。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GGtyzTc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGGtyzTc.jpg&h=83a60a94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同時，貓草的Nepetalactol化學物質塗在身上後，亦具備驅蚊效果。<br />\n<br />\n有科學家更利用是次研究的結果，申請了專利利用Nepetalactol製作驅蚊劑，同時亦正在進行研究貓草會否含有物質可對抗其他害蟲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SM6PSEX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSM6PSEX.png&h=4aa77ee5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n加多幅大頭像，希望各位可以入下面條link俾個like。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=CT6PJiTX903K6YLxhzu4TamkGRIJ7ARjMQoHd6uTSg0%3D&h=b9fcdc4c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「買一嚿/半嚿薯仔」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=CT6PJiTX903K6YLxhzu4TamkGRIJ7ARjMQoHd6uTSg0%3D&h=fdf89d35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n基於WhatsApp/Facebook等問題，IG將不會再作更新，只會寄居本土LIHKG及Penana。<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://advances.sciencemag.org/content/7/4/eabd9135\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fadvances.sciencemag.org%2Fcontent%2F7%2F4%2Feabd9135&d=CT6PJiTX903K6YLxhzu4TamkGRIJ7ARjMQoHd6uTSg0%3D&h=fd5af73d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://advances.sciencemag.org/content/7/4/eabd9135</a>"},{"pid":"83a2901f39101443fc51d48d73f90ed088f4a7fc","tid":2375136,"uid":35301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T20:32:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee584d115ef968eb980a5efb782ebb4b2914812d","tid":2375136,"uid":34119,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T20:34:56.000Z","msg":"有依隻驅蚊劑噴喺身到咪勁吸貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ea1650dd8d2cbe5b406fda20472fd6a10d07165","tid":2375136,"uid":38861,"like":7,"dislike":